data.title: RC Vehicles and Trains
data.meta_description: We specialize in RC cars, RC planes, and model trains. We've served you since 1973. Nationwide shipping is available. Get a free demonstration.
data.text:
At Hobby Haven, your hobbies are our business! We're proud to be your local spot for RC cars, trucks, planes, boats, trains, and more in Urbandale, IA. We've been serving you since 1973, and we're a family-owned business that offers personalized service and one-on-one experiences on every visit.

If you are a hobbyist, you'll love what we have in stock and our prices are competitive.

Call now or visit today! We offer shipping nationwide, and some products have factory warranties. Returns are accepted for like-new items within 30 days. Ask about our gift cards!
